Class AbstractIMAlgorithmRunner

Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractPRIRunner, AprioriCloseRunner, AprioriRareRunner, AprioriRunner, CharmBitSetRunner, CharmMFIRunner, CORIRunner, DCharmBitSetRunner, DEclatBitSetRunner, DEclatRunner, DefMeRunner, FPCloseRunner, FPGrowthRunner, FPMaxRunner, LCMFreqRunner, LCMRunner, ZartFrequentRunner, ZartRunner
public abstract class AbstractIMAlgorithmRunner extends Object implements AlgorithmRunnerInterface
An abstraction for frequent itemset mining. Contains all attributes frequent itemset mining runners need to function. Some runners will need to be given the filePath to the transaction database file, and others the TransactionDatabase object directly. That is why this class contains both the filePath and transactionDatabase attributes, which could seem redundant.
